freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Since 1st shot, thru last weekend, have had 4 headaches. i didn't have 4 headaches in the last year or before! Last 96 hrs, 2 separate sudden onset arm pain in injection arm, just like initially with the 2injections, but also radiating into shoulder.

not sure related, but will mention. earlier this wk, mon/tues, VERY tired and tues night, i had an incident of night sweats. I woke up freezing and drenched. I never did feel bad or like I had temp.  Today, i also felt LITTLE tired on/off.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: no other, just that headache comes/goes
